A day in Pienza, Tuscany 🇮🇹📍

This charming town, situated between Montepulciano and Montalcino has the most breathtaking views of Val d’Orcia (valley in the province of Siena, Tuscany). 

Highlight of my trip was visiting the place where a scene from one of my favorite movies, GLADIATOR was shot!! (Last two photos) 💯
